Great Morning Family! This is the day the Lord has made; I WILL rejoice and be glad in it! You take your life back by choosing to take your thoughts back. Even though we live in this natural realm, as Believers, we are not limited by this natural realm. We can tap into God’s power by making every thought line up with the Word of God. We don’t have to let circumstances control us. Instead, meditate on His Word and let His truth set you free!

Today, as you take captive every thought and boldly declare His promises over your life, you are setting yourself up for victory. You are positioning yourself to partake of His blessing. You are taking your life back and positioning yourself to embrace the abundant life He has prepared for you! Wake Up and Win this morning at 9am EST! Don't miss it!

Temi Otedola Finally Taking Driving Lessons .
.
.
.
21-year-old fashion blogger, Temi Otedola the daughter of Oil Magnate, Femi Otedola has finally started taking driving lessons after admitting to getting spoilt when it got to moving around. She has registered with Red Driving school in London and has given updates on her improvement on social media. She says its her new year resolution to learn how to drive.
__
Its imperative to note that Temi's big sis, Cuppy got a brand new G Wagon from her boyfriend, Victor Anichebe, after completing a similar driving training course with the same driving school last year. Some might wonder if her alleged lover, Mr Eazi can match such feat with a similar gift.
